-------------------
README
-------------------

- When pulling from Git...
 1. Have intelliJ up to date
 2. Have mongo installed
 3. Have NodeJS installed
 4. Have the mongo and NodeJS plugins installed
 5. Run: npm install -g @angular/cli (just in case)
 6. Run: ng new portal-app
 7. SPOT Check: npm install (just for peace of mind)

Once complete...
 1. cd to the built frontend (angular)
 2. CMD: ng server
 3. Web browser: localhost:4200